    if (!window.__CONFIG__) {
        return baseText;
    };
    var langObj = window.__CONFIG__.lang || {};
    
    if (baseText.indexOf('{productTitle}') > -1) {
        baseText = baseText.replace(/\{productTitle\}/g, langObj.productTitle)
    }
    return langObj[pathKey] || baseText;

function getUrlQuery(key) {
    var query = window.location.search.substring(1);
    var arr = query.split("&");

    for (var i=0; i<arr.length; i++) {
        var pair = arr[i].split("=");

        if (pair[0] === key) {
            return decodeURIComponent(pair[1]);
        }
    }
    return;
}

// 在 AP 部分场景中, 会根据滚动位置判断文档标题展示, 需要在产品标题/文档大标题间切换, 因此不使用 fileName 作为默认标题, 否则会产生标题闪动
function isOtlExclude() {
    var agent = window.navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase();
    // 这里取主要的 Pad

    var agent = window.navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase()
    var isMobile = /Android|webOS|iPhone|iPod|BlackBerry/i.test(agent)
    var container = document.querySelector('#loadError')
    var title = document.querySelector('#loadError .title')
    var btn = document.querySelector('#loadError .btn')
    var config = {
        title: _i18n("common.errorLoad.loadFail", "网络异常，请点击「刷新」重试"),
        btnText: _i18n("common.errorLoad.reload", "刷新"),
        className: 'loadFail'
    }
    container.className = config.className
    title.innerText = config.title
    btn.innerText = config.btnText
    btn.onclick = function () {
        sessionStorage.setItem('isReload', true)
        var reloadCdnHref = window.__WPSENV__.reloadCdnHref
        if (reloadCdnHref) {
            window.location.href = reloadCdnHref
        } else if (window._isHybrid) {
          window.__WPSENV__.backOnlinePage()
        }else {
          window.location.reload()
        }
    }
